Goal Tracking App
A simple web application to track weekly goals, monitor progress, and generate performance reports.

1. Features
Goal Management – Add, update, and delete goals.
Progress Tracking – Prevents progress from exceeding the target.
Weekly Reports – View and download JSON reports for the current week.



2. Tech Stack
Backend: Django, Django REST Framework.
Frontend: React, Axios.
Database: SQLite.


3. Setup Instructions
Backend Setup
bash
Copy code
python -m venv env
source env/bin/activate      # Linux/Mac
.\env\Scripts\activate       # Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
Frontend Setup
bash
Copy code
cd frontend
npm install
npm start


4. Usage
Open the app in your browser:
Copy code
http://localhost:3000
Create Goals – Add name, target, and progress.

Track Progress – Update goals and save changes.

View Report – Click Weekly Report for filtered goals.

Download Report – Click Download Report to save as JSON.

